item.title: 2017-90 - Random Tech Links
item.description: Currently, the focus is primarily on supporting the AWS cloud stack. LocalStack spins up the following core Cloud APIs on your local machine: API Gateway, Kinesis, DynamoDB, DynamoDB Streams, Elasticsearch, S3, Firehose, Lambda, SNS, SQS, Redshift
